Class ZSort

java.lang.Object
  com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.rendering.ZSort
All Implemented Interfaces:
LegendContentsChangedListener, IPersistence
public class ZSort
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPersistence, LegendContentsChangedListener

Class ZSort is used in order to store information about the symbols which are placed in the Z axis (because a level of symbols has been used).
